Entries.Description: Fixes issues with navigating, copying, and pasting to/from S3 paths that contain no-name directories.  See https://github.com/aws/aws-toolkit-visual-studio/issues/248
A link to the Troubleshooting Guide is now shown in the Publish to AWS experience when a deployment fails.
Amazon CloudWatch Logs Support: View, filter and store CloudWatch Logs resources from the AWS Explorer.
Added support to view CloudWatch Logs for Lambda functions and ECS Tasks.
